result:
.padding-large(style="height: 100%")
  div
    h2 Orders
  div.margin-y
  
    div(v-for="order in $store.state.myOrders").card.padding.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.margin-bottom-small
      div.flex
        div
          h5 DATE
          br
          span {{order.order_created}}
        div.margin-left-large
          h5 STATUS
          br
          span {{order.order_status}}
      div
        button(@click="$refs.order.show(order)") View Details

  modal(ref="order" inline-template)
    div
      transition(name='fade')
        #backdrop.fixed-fill(@click="toggle" v-show="visible")
      transition(name='fade')
        #modal(v-show="visible").card.fixed-center.flex.column.five-large.seven-medium.twelve-small.max-high
          div.flex.justify-space-between.align-center.wide
            h2.padding Order Details
            a.padding(@click="toggle"): fa(icon='times')
          hr
          div.padding.overflow-auto
            table.wide
              thead
                tr
                  th Print Size
                  th Filename
                  th Price
              tr
                td 8x10
                td DSC_0012
                td Php 100
              tr
                td 8x10
                td DSC_0012
                td Php 100
              tr  
                td 8x10
                td DSC_0012
                td Php 100
                
            div.flex.wide
              button.flex-grow Cancel Request
              button.flex-grow.margin-left-small For Pickup
